headline: Hologic (HOLX): Rethinking Valuation After a Recent 3-Month Share Price Rebound
summary: Hologic (HOLX) has been quietly grinding higher, with the stock up around 13% over the past 3 months as investors warm to its steady diagnostics and women’s health franchise after a mixed year. See our latest analysis for Hologic. Zooming out, that steady 3 month share price return of about 12.7% sits against a modest year to date gain and slightly negative 1 year total shareholder return, suggesting momentum is only just starting to turn in Hologic’s favor.
